Title: Designates a portion of the state highway system in the town of Haverstraw, county of Rockland, as the "Hector L. Soto Memorial Highway"
Summary: Designates a portion of the state highway system in the town of Haverstraw, county of Rockland, as the "Hector L. Soto Memorial Highway".
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a portion of the state highway system as the "Hector L. Soto Memorial Highway"
